Constructor Detail

MobileConnect.Builder

public MobileConnect.Builder(MobileConnectConfig config)
Start the builder, specifying the required configuration. The defaults applied by this builder are as follows:
  • scheduledExecutorService will use Executors.newScheduledThreadPool(int) with core size of DefaultOptions.THREAD_POOL_SIZE
  • httpClient will use default result of HttpClientBuilder
  • http timeout will be set to DefaultOptions.TIMEOUT_MS
  • restClient will use RestClient, with timeout and http client above
  • cache will use ConcurrentCache

Note that specifying a rest client instance will overrule any setting of http client, or timeout duration.

Parameters:
config - for Mobile Connect.
